    <div class=3D"wpd-comment-text">
    <p>Generator (G) =3D 6<br>
Prime (P) =3D 13</p>
<p>###</p>
<p>Alice Private =3D 8<br>
Bob Private =3D 3</p>
<p>###</p>
<p>Calculate public key (G^Private mod P)</p>
<p>Alice =3D 6=CB=868 mod 13 =3D 3<br>
Bob&nbsp;&nbsp;=3D 6=CB=863 mod 13 =3D 8</p>
<p>Alice will send to Bob =3D 3<br>
Bob will send to Alice =3D 8</p>
<p>###</p>
<p><span>Calculate Shared Secret (received^Private mod P)</span></p>
<p>Alice =3D 8=CB=868 mod 13 =3D 1<br>
Bob&nbsp;&nbsp;=3D 3=CB=863 mod 13 =3D 1</p>
<p>The Shared Secret is 1.</p>

