    <div class=3D"wpd-comment-text">
    <p>P =3D 5<br>
G =3D 4</p>
<p>Public key formula</p>
<p>(G pow Private) Mod P</p>
<p>A  choose 2 as private key</p>
<p>(4 pow 2) Mod 5<br>
16 | 5<br>
1(public key of A)</p>
<p>B choose 3 as private key<br>
(4 pow 3) Mod  5<br>
64 | 5<br>
4(public key of B)</p>
<p>To get shared secret formula</p>
<p>(public pow private) Mod P</p>
<p>A get shared secret as follows<br>
(4 pow 1) mod 5</p>
<p>4(A gets)</p>
<p>B get shared sectet as follows<br>
(1 pow 4) mod 5<br>
1(B gets)</p>

</div>
